rComments: The best professor I have ever had! Enjoy you retirement! You will be missed at U of T!
She made me love tax. I will miss her. Hope you enjoy your retirement years prof.

A highly knowledgeable professor who cared about her students;Facilitated student learning by requiring practice questions & quizzes to ensure students did not fall behind the course material.  Her textbook, Canadian Income Taxation, by William Buckwold & Joan Kitunen is a fabulous reference that I will continue to refer to in the future.
She inspired me to become the best tax pro I could possibly ever be.
